Invocation Name: couples trouble
des: How well do you know your other half? In this party game for friends or couples, players pair up, and Alexa quizzes each player on how well they know their partner. The partner judges the responses. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
